statements: SELECT * FROM competitors_seo_strategies;
SELECT competitor_name, analysis_date FROM competitors_seo_strategies;
SELECT competitor_id, seo_strategy FROM competitors_seo_strategies WHERE competitor_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM competitors_seo_strategies ORDER BY analysis_date DESC;
SELECT competitor_name, seo_strategy FROM competitors_seo_strategies WHERE competitor_name LIKE '%company%'
SELECT competitor_name, seo_strategy FROM competitors_seo_strategies WHERE competitor_id = 1;
SELECT competitor_name, analysis_date FROM competitors_seo_strategies WHERE competitor_id > 1 ORDER BY analysis_date DESC;
SELECT competitor_id, competitor_name, seo_strategy FROM competitors_seo_strategies WHERE analysis_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01';
SELECT competitor_name, COUNT(*) AS strategy_count FROM competitors_seo_strategies GROUP BY competitor_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 1;
SELECT competitor_id, competitor_name, seo_strategy, analysis_date FROM competitors_seo_strategies WHERE seo_strategy LIKE '%keyword%';
SELECT * FROM competitor_seo_strategies WHERE ranking_position > 3;
SELECT competitor_name, keyword FROM competitor_seo_strategies WHERE analysis_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT tactic_name, implementation_date, success_metric FROM own_seo_tactics WHERE success_metric LIKE '%organic%';
SELECT * FROM competitor_seo_strategies WHERE keyword = 'backlinks' ORDER BY analysis_date DESC;
SELECT ranking_position, competitor_name, keyword FROM competitor_seo_strategies WHERE competitor_name IN ('CompanyA', 'CompanyB');
SELECT competitor_name, keyword, ranking_position FROM competitor_seo_strategies WHERE ranking_position < 10 ORDER BY competitor_name DESC
SELECT tactic_name, implementation_date, success_metric FROM own_seo_tactics WHERE implementation_date >= '2021-01-01' ORDER BY implementation_date ASC
SELECT keyword, COUNT(*) as num_occurrences FROM competitor_seo_strategies GROUP BY keyword HAVING num_occurrences > 1 ORDER BY num_occurrences DESC
SELECT competitor_name, MAX(ranking_position) as highest_ranking FROM competitor_seo_strategies GROUP BY competitor_name ORDER BY highest_ranking DESC
SELECT tactic_name, notes FROM own_seo_tactics WHERE success_metric LIKE '%improved%' ORDER BY tactic_name ASC
SELECT * FROM competitor_data;
SELECT competitor_id, competitor_name FROM competitor_data ORDER BY competitor_id DESC;
SELECT keyword, search_volume FROM keyword_performance WHERE search_volume > 1000 AND organic_ranking < 10;
SELECT backlink_url, domain_authority FROM backlink_quality ORDER BY domain_authority DESC;
SELECT competitor_name, COUNT(competitor_id) AS num_keywords FROM keyword_performance kp JOIN competitor_data cd ON kp.competitor_id = cd.competitor_id GROUP BY competitor_name;
SELECT * FROM competitor_data;
SELECT competitor_name, keyword_analysis FROM competitor_data WHERE competitor_id = 1;
SELECT keyword, search_volume FROM keyword_performance ORDER BY search_volume DESC;
SELECT competitor_name, domain_authority FROM competitor_data JOIN backlink_quality ON competitor_data.competitor_id = backlink_quality.competitor_id;
SELECT competitor_name, backlink_url FROM competitor_data JOIN backlink_quality ON competitor_data.competitor_id = backlink_quality.competitor_id WHERE domain_authority > 50;
SELECT * FROM competitors;
SELECT competitor_name, competitor_website FROM competitors;
SELECT keyword_name, search_volume FROM keywords WHERE competition_level > 5;
SELECT competitor_name, position, date FROM competitors INNER JOIN rankings ON competitors.competitor_id = rankings.competitor_id;
SELECT competitor_name, backlinks, domain_authority, page_authority FROM competitors LEFT JOIN seo_metrics ON competitors.competitor_id = seo_metrics.competitor_id;
SELECT * FROM competitors WHERE competitor_id = 1;
SELECT competitor_name, competitor_website FROM competitors WHERE competitor_name ILIKE 'A%' ORDER BY competitor_name DESC;

SELECT competitor_name, keyword_name, position FROM competitors c JOIN rankings r ON c.competitor_id = r.competitor_id JOIN keywords k ON r.keyword_id = k.keyword_id WHERE position <= 3 ORDER BY competitor_name, position ASC;

SELECT c.competitor_name, k.keyword_name, r.position, r.date FROM competitors c JOIN rankings r ON c.competitor_id = r.competitor_id JOIN keywords k ON r.keyword_id = k.keyword_id WHERE r.date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY r.date DESC;

SELECT c.competitor_name, m.backlinks, m.domain_authority, m.page_authority FROM competitors c JOIN seo_metrics m ON c.competitor_id = m.competitor_id WHERE m.page_authority > 50 ORDER BY m.page_authority DESC, m.backlinks ASC;
SELECT * FROM competitors;
SELECT competitor_name, seo_strategy FROM competitors WHERE id = 1;
SELECT competitor_name, seo_strategy FROM competitors ORDER BY competitor_name ASC;
SELECT keyword_name, search_volume FROM keywords WHERE search_volume > 1000;
SELECT competitor_name, traffic_source, traffic_count FROM competitors JOIN website_traffic ON competitors.id = website_traffic.competitor_id;
SELECT competitor_name, seo_strategy FROM competitors WHERE id = 1;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_backlinks FROM backlinks WHERE competitor_id = 3;
SELECT keyword_name, search_volume FROM keywords ORDER BY search_volume DESC;
SELECT competitor_name, rank_date, ranking_position FROM competitors INNER JOIN ranking_history ON competitors.id = ranking_history.competitor_id WHERE ranking_position < 10;
SELECT DISTINCT traffic_source FROM website_traffic WHERE traffic_count > 1000;
